xfonts-75dpi (1:1.0.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream releases for X11R7.5:
    - font-adobe-75dpi 1.0.1
    - font-bh-75dpi 1.0.1
    - font-bh-lucidatypewriter-75dpi 1.0.1
    - font-bitstream-75dpi 1.0.1
